<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Katie Price refused to let her broken feet get her down on Tuesday as she headed out for lunch with her boyfriend Carl Woods. </p>

<p>The glamour model, 42, who is unable to walk while she recovers from her eight-hour surgery, was picked up and carried by Carl, 31, into the restaurant in Essex.</p>

<p>It comes after sources close to Katie said it 'wouldn't be a surprise' if they wed soon, after she took the car businessman's surname on a personalised number plate for her mobility scooter.</p>

<p>Doting boyfriend: Katie Price refused to let her broken feet get her down on Tuesday as she headed out for lunch with her beau Carl Woods</p>

<p>Despite her obvious setback, Katie maintained a glamorous appearance with her full face of make-up, poker straight hair and silk navy top. </p>

<p>She teamed the look with ripped denim jeans, while the boot casts went up to below the knee. </p>

<p>Carl, meanwhile, was casually-clad in a black T-shirt, jeans and trainers. </p>

<p>Mwah! The couple couldn't keep their hands off each other as they sat down for an alfresco lunch and were pictured passionately kissing</p>

<p>Swept off her feet: The glamour model, 42, who is unable to walk while she recovers from her eight-hour surgery, was picked up and carried by Carl, 31, into the restaurant in Essex</p>

